thread.title: Why Corporate Profits May Be Weaker Than They Seem

author: Justin Lahart
title: Why Corporate Profits May Be Weaker Than They Seem
text:
According to companies, profits were great in the first quarter. According to government statistics, not so much.
Profits for companies in the S&P 500 grew a stunning 26.3% in the first quarter compared to a year earlier, according to Thomson Reuters I/B/E/S. That measure, which is used by investors, benefited from a strong global...
